{"tid":516463,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日終於忍唔到口鬧啲廢老！","createTime":"2018-01-01T12:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T13:06:02.000Z","uid":27396,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ed5593390daee07ee6b9ef205b66c0d43b4687ce","tid":516463,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"係我屋企環境嘅影響下，我不嬲都好尊敬老一輩，果啲咩雨傘運動啊，示威啊，我一次都冇去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係今日終於發現佢地好自私！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我平時有健開身，今日又係最憎嘅leg day<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁我因爲遲起身又趕住操，所以係未食野，結果操完之後頭勁暈，馬上去到公園到抖下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我果時左邊有個婆婆，我見佢個嘴郁下郁下，唔洗問啦，一定食緊糖，咁我想問佢拎一粒食果時，佢冇啦啦發脾氣鬧我，當時我雖然頭暈，但係都明白老人家積蓄得咁小，佢地都係想慳啲用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我去到7仔到買左一排能得利，好硬好痴牙果隻軟糖係到食，希望咬耐啲，可以分散注意力，唔好再咁頭暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食食下諗起個婆婆咁慘，中午冇飯食係到食糖，我馬上去搵返佢，但係可能佢粒糖真係好好食，佢唔多應我，最後我將成排能得利一粒一粒慢慢喂佢，但係最後佢竟然追住我黎打，我嬲到好大聲鬧左佢一獲，走果時仲見佢眼濕濕咁，係到扮可憐！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以話啲廢老一啲都唔識知恩圖報！</span></span>"},{"pid":"35fa76608cafbab12ebd6ec394de322abb38700f","tid":516463,"uid":146917,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"Too long didn&rsquo;t read"},{"pid":"2ff5f648e4b4d8088ddb7b98578c23935be3bb12","tid":516463,"uid":20563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:25:02.000Z","msg":"成篇其實係up 乜柒"},{"pid":"6a3fa44ebf6abf76f329ebe232ae395a28d73500","tid":516463,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:26:06.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cb0381de515b613dd4431148b06ba1b095f1b9","tid":516463,"uid":106149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"長到咁 簡約少少啦 大佬"},{"pid":"9e2ecc6ff3069c3dcb33ffbe29f35e9c2facbcdc","tid":516463,"uid":103380,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:32:02.000Z","msg":"幽默感真係勉強唔黎架⋯"},{"pid":"4987dfc6d8a2813500865c28ee656a081f68c722","tid":516463,"uid":119783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:32:34.000Z","msg":"想表達D咩"},{"pid":"b47aedd10145a73bbccc776dc4318903c9133aef","tid":516463,"uid":81575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:34:41.000Z","msg":"樓主2018年目標改善表達能力"},{"pid":"ad75bdade80d2aeb765509fc2189058c297ee6d1","tid":516463,"uid":112528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔知樓主想表達啲乜"},{"pid":"3049e7390081bf0b4106555f3c3593f509f27292","tid":516463,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"蟻多嬲死象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed211d55ad1c4ad96e659975acfcb7f650b3fab8","tid":516463,"uid":75636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:05:58.000Z","msg":"樓主都係出番IQ題啦"},{"pid":"848287532d39049441bc25622501b8ea65c56f17","tid":516463,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:06:02.000Z","msg":"巴打中文作文一定好低分"}]}